block content 
    h1.bd-title#content Input group
    p.bd-lead Easily extend form controls by adding text, buttons, or button groups on either side of textual inputs, custom selects, and custom file inputs.
    h2#basic-example Basic example
    p
        | Place one add-on or button on either side of an input. You may also place one on both sides of an input. Remember to place 
        code.highlighter-rouge <label>
        | s outside the input group.
    .bd-example
        +input-group('@','','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','textUsername','Username')
        +input-group('','@example.com','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','textRecipientUsername','Recipient\'s username')

        label(for='basic-url') Your vanity URL
        +input-group('https://example.com/users/','','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','basic-url')
        +input-group('$','.00','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','amount')
        +input-group('With textarea')
            +textarea()
    
    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.js.
                +input-group('@','','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','textUsername','Username')
                +input-group('','@example.com','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','textRecipientUsername','Recipient\'s username')

                label(for='basic-url') Your vanity URL
                +input-group('https://example.com/users/','','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','basic-url')
                +input-group('$','.00','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','amount')
                +input-group('With textarea')
                    +textarea()
    h2#sizing Sizing
    p
        | Add the relative form sizing classes to the 
        code.highlighter-rouge .input-group
        |  itself and contents within will automatically resize—no need for repeating the form control size classes on each element.
    p
        strong Sizing on the individual input group elements isn’t supported.
    .bd-example
        +input-group('Small','','mb-3','sm')
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')
        +input-group('Default','','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','textDefault')
        +input-group('Large','','mb-3','lg')
            +input-simple('text','textLarge')
    
    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.js.
                +input-group('Small','','mb-3','sm')
                    +input-simple('text','textSmall')
                +input-group('Default','','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','textDefault')
                +input-group('Large','','mb-3','lg')
                    +input-simple('text','textLarge')

    h2#checkboxes-and-radios Checkboxes and radios
    p
        | Place any checkbox or radio option within an input group’s addon instead of text.
    .bd-example
        +input-group('<input type="checkbox" aria-label="Checkbox for following text input">','','mb-3')
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')
        +input-group('<input type="radio" aria-label="Radio button for following text input">')
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')

    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.js.
                +input-group('&lt;input type="checkbox" aria-label="Checkbox for following text input"&gt;','','mb-3')
                    +input-simple('text','textSmall')
                +input-group('&lt;input type="radio" aria-label="Radio button for following text input"&gt;')
                    +input-simple('text','textSmall')

    h2#multiple-inputs Multiple inputs
    p
        | While multiple 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;input&gt;
        | s are supported visually, validation styles are only available for input groups with a single 
        code.highlighter-rouge &lt;input&gt;
        | .
    .bd-example
        +input-group('First and last name')
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')

    figure.highlight
