    h2#multiple-addons Multiple addons
    p Multiple add-ons are supported and can be mixed with checkbox and radio input versions.
    .bd-example
        .input-group.mb-3
            .input-group-prepend
                span.input-group-text $
                span.input-group-text 0.00
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')
        .input-group
            +input-simple('text','textSmall')
            .input-group-append
                span.input-group-text $
                span.input-group-text 0.00

    figure.highlight
        pre
            code.js.
                .input-group.mb-3
